<body>
    <%-include('header')%>
        <main id="body">
            <section class="py-3">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-9 mx-auto">
                            <article class="bg-content p-3 rounded">
                                <div class="about-content">
                                    <h1 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">About HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM Guide</h1>
                                    <p>We are an independent fan team that curates news, platform links, spoiler-free
                                        tips, and
                                        accessibility resources for <strong>HER TREES : PUZZLE DREAM</strong>, the
                                        monochrome
                                        point-and-click adventure developed and published by Stone. The official game
                                        launched on
                                        <strong>February 11, 2026</strong>, and our guide exists solely to help players
                                        understand what to expect before visiting the storefront or purchasing the
                                        title.
                                    </p>

                                    <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Who We Are</h2>
                                    <p>Our volunteers are long-time puzzle fans who appreciate the HER TREES
                                        trilogy&rsquo;s
                                        hand-drawn aesthetic and non-verbal storytelling. This site is not operated by
                                        Stone and
                                        does not replace the official channels—it simply gathers verified public
                                        information in
                                        one place for the convenience of the community.</p>

                                    <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">What You Will Find Here</h2>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Feature breakdowns that explain mechanics, playtime expectations, and
                                            accessibility
                                            options without spoiling puzzle solutions.</li>
                                        <li>Updates on platform availability, controller support, and storefront links
                                            so you can
                                            jump directly to the official release.</li>
                                        <li>Context about the broader HER TREES franchise, including mentions of <em>HER
                                                TREES:
                                                First Puzzle</em> and <em>HER TREES: THE PUZZLE HOUSE</em> for players
                                            who want
                                            to experience the earlier chapters.</li>
                                    </ul>

                                    <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Respect for Stone&rsquo;s Work</h2>
                                    <p>All characters, artwork, and trademarks related to HER TREES remain the sole
                                        property of
                                        Stone. We never host proprietary downloads, paid assets, or soundtrack files,
                                        and we
                                        always link back to the official store pages to ensure that purchases and
                                        reviews support
                                        the creators.</p>

                                    <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">How We Source Information</h2>
                                    <p>Details published on this site are compiled from official developer
                                        announcements,
                                        verified press materials, and publicly available storefront descriptions. When
                                        we
                                        summarize outside coverage we provide attribution and avoid copying text
                                        verbatim.</p>

                                    <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-2">Staying Connected</h2>
                                    <p>If you spot an error, would like us to highlight a new accessibility resource, or
                                        need a
                                        clarification, reach us at <a
                                            href="mailto:support@hertrees.co">support@hertrees.co</a>
                                        or through the <a href="/contactus">Contact Us</a> page. We typically respond
                                        within two
                                        business days.</p>
                                </div>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
